overview: Get ready for another Open House with the 13th installment of “Lesbian House Hunters”! Its house hunting with a twist when Jelena Jensen is the real estate agent on duty and making these lesbians go on the hunt for each other! Instead of asking about the square footage of the property Chanel Preston, Lily Labeau, Scarlett Sage and their friends can't wait to get to the bedroom to use their tongues, hands and tongues to not only make an offer; but seal the deal over an orgasm or two.
tagline: Lesbians go on the hunt for each other!
title: Lesbian House Hunters 13
